{"tha-ap25:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap25:0.2":"Subhutivagga ","tha-ap25:0.3":"3 Tisaranagamaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap25:1.1":"“Nagare candavatiya, ","tha-ap25:1.2":"matuupatthako ahum; ","tha-ap25:1.3":"Andha mata pita mayham, ","tha-ap25:1.4":"te posemi aham tada. ","tha-ap25:2.1":"Rahogato nisiditva, ","tha-ap25:2.2":"evam cintesaham tada; ","tha-ap25:2.3":"Posento matapitaro, ","tha-ap25:2.4":"pabbajjam na labhamaham. ","tha-ap25:3.1":"Mahandhakarapihita, ","tha-ap25:3.2":"tividhaggihi dayhare; ","tha-ap25:3.3":"Etadise bhave jate, ","tha-ap25:3.4":"natthi koci vinayako. ","tha-ap25:4.1":"Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap25:4.2":"dippati dani sasanam; ","tha-ap25:4.3":"Sakka uddharitum atta, ","tha-ap25:4.4":"punnakamena jantuna. ","tha-ap25:5.1":"Uggayha tini sarane, ","tha-ap25:5.2":"paripunnani gopayim; ","tha-ap25:5.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap25:5.4":"patimokkhami duggatim. ","tha-ap25:6.1":"Nisabho nama samano, ","tha-ap25:6.2":"buddhassa aggasavako; ","tha-ap25:6.3":"Tamaham upagantvana, ","tha-ap25:6.4":"saranagamanam gahim. ","tha-ap25:7.1":"Vassasatasahassani, ","tha-ap25:7.2":"ayu vijjati tavade; ","tha-ap25:7.3":"Tavata saranagamanam, ","tha-ap25:7.4":"paripunnam agopayim. ","tha-ap25:8.1":"Carime vattamanamhi, ","tha-ap25:8.2":"saranam tam anussarim; ","tha-ap25:8.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap25:8.4":"tavatimsam agacchaham. ","tha-ap25:9.1":"Devalokagato santo, ","tha-ap25:9.2":"punnakammasamahito; ","tha-ap25:9.3":"Yam desam upapajjami, ","tha-ap25:9.4":"attha hetu labhamaham. ","tha-ap25:10.1":"Disasu pujito homi, ","tha-ap25:10.2":"tikkhapanno bhavamaham; ","tha-ap25:10.3":"Sabbe devanuvattanti, ","tha-ap25:10.4":"amitabhogam labhamaham. ","tha-ap25:11.1":"Suvannavanno sabbattha, ","tha-ap25:11.2":"patikanto bhavamaham; ","tha-ap25:11.3":"Mittanam acalo homi, ","tha-ap25:11.4":"yaso abbhuggato mamam. ","tha-ap25:12.1":"Asitikkhattu devindo, ","tha-ap25:12.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap25:12.3":"Dibbasukham anubhavim, ","tha-ap25:12.4":"accharahi purakkhato. ","tha-ap25:13.1":"Pancasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap25:13.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap25:13.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap25:13.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap25:14.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap25:14.2":"punnakammasamahito; ","tha-ap25:14.3":"Pure savatthiyam jato, ","tha-ap25:14.4":"mahasale suaddhake. ","tha-ap25:15.1":"Nagara nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap25:15.2":"darakehi purakkhato; ","tha-ap25:15.3":"Hasakhiddasamangiham, ","tha-ap25:15.4":"sangharamam upagamim. ","tha-ap25:16.1":"Tatthaddasasim samanam, ","tha-ap25:16.2":"vippamuttam nirupadhim; ","tha-ap25:16.3":"So me dhammamadesesi, ","tha-ap25:16.4":"sarananca adasi me. ","tha-ap25:17.1":"Soham sutvana saranam, ","tha-ap25:17.2":"saranam me anussarim; ","tha-ap25:17.3":"Ekasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap25:17.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap25:18.1":"Jatiya sattame vasse, ","tha-ap25:18.2":"arahattamapapunim; ","tha-ap25:18.3":"Upasampadayi buddho, ","tha-ap25:18.4":"gunamannaya cakkhuma. ","tha-ap25:19.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap25:19.2":"saranani agacchaham; ","tha-ap25:19.3":"Tato me sukatam kammam, ","tha-ap25:19.4":"phalam dassesi me idha. ","tha-ap25:20.1":"Sugopitam me saranam, ","tha-ap25:20.2":"manasam suppanihitam; ","tha-ap25:20.3":"Anubhotva yasam sabbam, ","tha-ap25:20.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap25:21.1":"Yesam sotavadhanatthi, ","tha-ap25:21.2":"sunotha mama bhasato; ","tha-ap25:21.3":"Aham vo kathayissami, ","tha-ap25:21.4":"samam dittham padam mama. ","tha-ap25:22.1":"‘Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap25:22.2":"vattate jinasasanam; ","tha-ap25:22.3":"Amata vadita bheri, ","tha-ap25:22.4":"sokasallavinodana. ","tha-ap25:23.1":"Yathasakena thamena, ","tha-ap25:23.2":"punnakkhette anuttare; ","tha-ap25:23.3":"Adhikaram kareyyatha, ","tha-ap25:23.4":"passayissatha nibbutim. ","tha-ap25:24.1":"Paggayha tini sarane, ","tha-ap25:24.2":"pancasilani gopiya; ","tha-ap25:24.3":"Buddhe cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap25:24.4":"dukkhassantam karissatha. ","tha-ap25:25.1":"Samma dhammam bhavetvana, ","tha-ap25:25.2":"Silani parigopiya; ","tha-ap25:25.3":"Aciram arahattam vo, ","tha-ap25:25.4":"Sabbepi papunissatha. ","tha-ap25:26.1":"Tevijjo iddhipattomhi, ","tha-ap25:26.2":"cetopariyakovido; ","tha-ap25:26.3":"Savako te mahavira, ","tha-ap25:26.4":"sarano vandati satthuno’. ","tha-ap25:27.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap25:27.2":"saranam buddhassa gacchaham; ","tha-ap25:27.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap25:27.4":"saranam gamane phalam. ","tha-ap25:28.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap25:28.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap25:28.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap25:28.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap25:29.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tisaranagamaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap25:30.1":"Tisaranagamaniyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}